Package: tailqr
Type: Package
Title: 'Fit Mixture of Quantile Regression and GPDs'
Version: 1.0
Date: 2018-05-24
Author: Gregory Bopp
Maintainer: Gregory Bopp <your@email.com>
Description: This package is used for fitting a quantile regression model to The Large Ensemble Community Project temperature data (http://www.cesm.ucar.edu/projects/community-projects/LENS/) using a periodic basis in time for the bulk of the distribution, and a mixture of GPDs in the tails.
